1. *Nam* je lako da se lako dogovorimo. (It is easy for us to agree.)
2. Nismo imali dovoljno vremena da svi *nam* uspeju. (We didn't have enough time for all of us to succeed.)
3. Želim da svi *nam* budemo srećni. (I want for all of us to be happy.)
4. *Nam* se obično dogovaramo bez problema. (We usually agree without any problems.)
5. Postavio je pitanje *nam*, ali nismo znali da odgovorimo. (He asked us a question, but we didn't know how to answer.)